    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Three factors achieve Gradation 3 (discretization error exceeds requirement). Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate RHI predictions within 15% of experimental data across all five COU operating points. Turbulence model uncertainty quantified and bounded. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device under the stated COU. Acceptance criterion RH < 1 satisfied at all operating points with adequate margin.",
